MacOS Install:
Open Terminal (launchpad -> type in terminal):
Install Brew:
https://brew.sh/
/bin/bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/HEAD/install.sh)"
brew install curl
brew install php
To Troubleshoot brew:
brew doctor

