Get IP address:
If you enter the command ‚Äúifconfig‚Äù in the terminal, all information will be displayed. You can also use the commands ‚Äúip addr‚Äù or ‚Äúip a‚Äù
Grep 1 liner for IP address:
ip addr show eth0 | grep inet | awk '{ print $2; }' | sed 's/\/.*$//'

